https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500null This is only a teaser of the full concert "Live at Folsom Field" but the live versions of these two fairly new songs, "Bartender" and "When The World Ends" only leave the viewer wanting more Dave. Any fan should check out "Folsom Field" for it is a great concert, mixing the very old material with the very new stuff. Dave Matthews Band: Some Other Stuff
